    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a reliable daily driver for someone who isn't concerned with cosmetic perfection. The exterior shows its age with some noticeable scratches, a few small door dings, and minor paint thinning on the hood. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows visible wear and some staining on the carpets. Mechanically, the car runs and drives well, though it will likely need some routine maintenance items like new tires and a brake service in the near future. It is a solid, functional vehicle that has been used regularly and is priced according to its current state.",
