    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I am honestly so sad to be parting with this beauty, but it's time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it still has that 'new car' feel and looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I've been super meticulous about keeping it spotless and staying on top of every little bit of maintenance. It drives like an absolute dream! If you're looking for a ride that's basically perfect without the brand-new price tag, you've gotta come take a look. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
